  "description": "This individual presents as an undead remnant, marked by zombie skin and the desiccated shrink of facial tissue around the jaw. Gray eyes sit deep under a pronounced brow ridge, and black hair persists in sparse, broken clumps along the scalp. The frame is narrow and tendon-forward, with forearms etched by old cut-marks that read as pre-mortem labor injury rather than recent violence. Dentition remains intact but uneven, lending the mouth a fixed, graveyard rictus typical of long-exposed dead.",
